Nukta $D$ na $E$ zinachaguliwa kwenye upande $BC$ wa pembetatu $ABC$ hivyo kwamba $E$ iko kati ya $B$ na $D$ na $BE=1$, $ED=DC=3$. Ikiwa $\angle BAD=\angle EAC=90^\circ$, eneo la $ABC$ linaweza kuonyeshwa kama $\tfrac{p\sqrt q}r$, ambapo $p$ na $r$ ni nambari kamili chanya zenye uwiano mkuu wa moja na $q$ ni nambari kamili chanya ambayo haigawanyiki na mraba wa nambari msingi yoyote. Hesabu $p+q+r$.

[asy]
import olympiad;
size(200);
defaultpen(linewidth(0.7)+fontsize(11pt));
pair D = origin, E = (3,0), C = (-3,0), B = (4,0);
path circ1 = arc(D,3,0,180), circ2 = arc(B/2,2,0,180);
pair A = intersectionpoint(circ1, circ2);
draw(E--A--C--B--A--D);
label(" $A$ ",A,N);
label(" $B$ ",B,SE);
label(" $C$ ",C,SW);
label(" $D$ ",D,S);
label(" $E$ ",E,S);
[/asy]

